<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.1/css/bootstrap.min.css'>
    <title>What is the angle between the hour and minute hand?</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div class='container'>
        <h1>Clock Angle Calculator</h1>
        <p>Enter an hour and a minute and we will calculate the angle between the hands.</p>
        <form action='/view_angle'>
            <div class='form-group'>
              <label for='hour'>Hour:</label>
              <input id='hour' name='hour' class='form-control' type='number'>
            </div>
            <div class='form-group'>
              <label for='minute'>Minute:</label>
              <input id='minute' name='minute' class='form-control' type='number'>
            </div>
            <button type='submit' class='btn-success'>Submit</button>
        </form>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
